00:40:15.639 --> 00:40:17.159
Kahit isang taon...

00:40:18.480 --> 00:40:19.480
...tatlong buwan...

00:40:20.440 --> 00:40:22.199
...o mas kaunting oras pa...

00:40:25.639 --> 00:40:27.119
...huwag tayong mag-alala.

00:40:27.679 --> 00:40:29.159
Maging masaya tayo araw-araw.

00:40:30.159 --> 00:40:32.239
Pangako ko na lagi akong nasa tabi mo.

00:40:49.800 --> 00:40:50.880
Sabihin mo.

00:40:53.239 --> 00:40:54.599
Mas magiging maayos ang pakiramdam kapag nasabi mo na.

00:40:56.719 --> 00:40:57.960
Nandito lang ako.

00:41:22.079 --> 00:41:23.239
Anong nangyayari dito?

00:41:27.039 --> 00:41:28.320
Weiguo, siya...

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:30.920
...parang hindi tama.

00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:32.880
Anong ibig mong sabihin, hindi tama?

00:41:35.559 --> 00:41:36.719
Suot niya ang salamin niya.

00:41:38.079 --> 00:41:40.800
Ito ang sabi ng doktor...

00:41:41.800 --> 00:41:44.119
...tungkol sa isang bagay na pumipindot sa kanya...

00:41:44.119 --> 00:41:45.239
...nerbiyos na optiko.

00:41:45.800 --> 00:41:47.360
Dinidiinan nito ang optic nerve.

00:41:48.840 --> 00:41:50.079
Ano ang gagawin natin kung gayon?

